    <p>
        <h5 style="color:brown">Things To Do at Paradise Beach, Puducherry:</h5>

        Considered as one of the best sightseeing places in Puducherry, Paradise Beach offers several things to keep you engaged all the time. So, whether you are an adult, a child, or an old-age tourist, you’ll surely find something of your interest on this beach. A few of the must-to-do activities include:
        <div style="padding:4px;"></div>
        <h5 style="color:brown">Play Your Favourite Beach Sports:</h5> Try your hand at your favorite beach sport from football, volleyball, cricket, or badminton to bring plenty of memories back home. The soft golden sand of this beach makes it an ideal location for outdoor sports lovers to engage in beach sports. You can either choose to bring your own ball from home or simply ask the beach authorities for one.
        <div style="padding:4px;"></div>
        <h5 style="color:brown">Indulge in Water Adventures:</h5> Choose from a diverse range of adventurous activities such as Canoeing, Kayaking, and Jet Skiing to explore the adventurous side in you. Please note that the beach is quite deep, so it is important to take all safety precautions before starting any activity. Also, these activities are not designed to be available 365 days on the beach. Hence, check with the authorities first before heading to this beach in case you are coming here for adventure activities only.
        <div style="padding:4px;"></div>
        <h5 style="color:brown">Photography:</h5> Haven for photographers, Paradise Beach offers innumerable opportunities to capture some amazing photographs that you’ll cherish forever. It has attractions beyond your imagination. Here you can take pictures of a beautiful landscape along with many inspiring sights that look stunning when clicked throughout the boat ride.
        <div style="padding:4px;"></div>
        <h5 style="color:brown">Walking:</h5> How about enjoying a leisure walk with your partner in the evening? Yes, it’s indeed the nicest thing to do every time you are on this beach. All you need is to take out your sandals or shoes and enjoy a short stroll with bare feet along the length of the beach. And when you get tired, you can sit on the soft sand and experience some ME time in privacy.
        <div style="padding:4px;"></div>
        <h5 style="color:brown">Eating:</h5> Treat your taste buds with a wide variety of mouthwatering dishes served at the beach shacks. The local vendors at Paradise Beach sell some hot bhajjis that are a must-try. You can also order from a large assortment of beverages to complement your meal. Don’t forget to sip the fresh and tender coconut water here.


    </p>

